column1: Baby Barnaby's////I had the Green Eggs and my bf had the Pink and White Scramble. I cannot speak in enough volumes to how delicious the Green Eggs were -- the flavors of spinach
column3: artichoke topped with jack cheese were heavenly. What also made me choose this plate was the amount of food listed in the description---chicken apple sausage
